            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Generous."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I have a responsibility to help and protect the less fortunate. (Good)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Loyal."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " My word, once given, is my bond. (Lawful)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Callous."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I am unconcerned with any negative effects my actions may have on the lives and fortunes of others. (Evil)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Impulsive."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I follow my heart. (Chaotic)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Ignorant."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Explanations bore me. (Neutral)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "element",
                    "tag": "strong",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Isolationist."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " I am concerned with the fortunes of my friends and family. Others must see to themselves. (Any)"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h3",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Mulmaster Aristocrat Bond"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "table",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "d6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Bond"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "1"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "I have dedicated my wealth and my talents to the service of one of the city's many temples."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "2"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "My family and I are loyal supporters of High Blade Jaseen Drakehorn. Our fortunes are inexorably tied to hers. I would do anything to support her."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "3"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Like many families who were close to High Blade Selfaril Uoumdolphin, mine has suffered greatly since his fall. We honor his memory in secret."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "4"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "My family plotted with Rassendyll Uoumdolphin's brother. Betrayal is the quickest route to power."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "5"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Wealth and power are nothing. Fulfillment can only be found in artistic expression."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "6"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "It's not how you feel, who you know, or what you can do - it's how you look, and I look fabulous."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "h3",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "strong",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Mulmaster Aristocrat Flaws"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "element",
        "tag": "table",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "element",
            "tag": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "element",
                "tag": "th",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
